sub_title: IT Help Desk Technician en Samskip
summary:
I have extensive experience working in Installation and maintenance of security cameras, recording equipment (DVR), administration of the same. Also in technical support either software or hardware (IT ESSENTIALS Certification) Knowledge of Linux, Windows, MacOS. In the year 2017 and 2018 I finished my CCNA certification, CCNA Security. Currently studying MOC: Installation, storage and computing with Windows Server 2016.
Always looking to grow as a person and professionally.
